{"lastModified":1768317557031,"uri":"c::18121026674::vessel::1a3f9c60-6fa8-11ef-a235-5bf50187fc40","yachtType":["Motor"],"description":"Operating Area: Sardinia\n\nMERRY FISHER, RENT A MOTORBOAT IN SARDINIA TO ENJOY THE SEA. Passion and innovation merge to realize this jewelry of the sea.\nThis boat was created to make your onboard life easy. Actually thanks to a brilliant layout project this yacht has amazing living solution. So, inside we have 3 roomy cabins, 1 wide bathroom with shower box, a fully equipped kitchen and a comfortable dinette. Moreover the dinette sofa can easily transformed in a comfy double bed. Perfect match between elegance, technology and luxury, the Merry Fisher 1095 gives amazing spaces to who loves the outside life. The Merry Fisher 1095 outside Layout, thanks to its huge soft beds on the prow, the cozy seats on the stern and to the spacious sides platform, reminds, for comfy and spaciousness, a bigger yacht. The Merry Fisher 1095 is a motorboat for rent that attracts attentions on the sea for its sporty and smart design. The driving console, designed for the real sea lovers, makes the Merry Fisher 1095 the best yacht to sailing with. Moreover its phenomenal “Delta” hull allows to cruise with absolute relax and the outboard engines guarantee quiet, low petrol consume and easy mooring. The Merry Fisher 1095 represents the perfect solution to whomever is looking for an unforgettable vacation in Sardinia with a boat for rent!","blueprint":{"name":"MERRY FISHER 1095","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::1a3f9c60-6fa8-11ef-a235-5bf50187fc40::assets::77938f10-6fa9-11ef-becd-531601b97abf/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::1a3f9c60-6fa8-11ef-a235-5bf50187fc40::assets::779340f0-6fa9-11ef-becd-531601b97abf/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::1a3f9c60-6fa8-11ef-a235-5bf50187fc40::assets::7791e160-6fa9-11ef-becd-531601b97abf/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::1a3f9c60-6fa8-11ef-a235-5bf50187fc40::assets::7